<subSubSection pageId="44" pageNumber="439" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="44.[1396,2604,2651,3471]" pageId="44" pageNumber="439">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1398,1532,3202,3235]" pageId="44" pageNumber="439">Breeding.</emphasis>
lactating Medellin Small-eared Shrews have been captured in February, and a pregnant female with two embryos was captured in October.
</paragraph>
